k" href="./Mongolia" title="Mongolia">Mongolia</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Successor</th><td><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ögedei_Khan" title="Ögedei Khan">Ögedei Khan</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;background-color: #e4dcf6;line-height:normal;padding:0.2em 0.2em"><div style="height: 4px; width:100%;"></div></th></tr><tr><th scope="row">Born</th><td>Temüjin<sup about="#mwt544" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-2" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"group":"note"},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-2"}}'><a href="./Genghis_Khan#cite_note-2" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 1;" data-mw-group="note"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[note 1]</span></a></sup><br/>likely 1162<sup about="#mwt207" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-birth_3-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"birth"}}'><a href="./Genghis_Khan#cite_note-birth-3" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 2;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[2]</span></a></sup><br/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Khentii_Mountains" title="Khentii Mountains">Khentii Mountains</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Khamag_Mongol" title="Khamag Mongol">Khamag Mongol</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Died</th><td>August 18, 1227<sup about="#mwt530" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-4" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-4"}}'><a href="./Genghis_Khan#cite_note-4" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 3;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[3]</span></a></sup> (aged 64–65)<br/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Yinchuan" title="Yinchuan">Yinchuan</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Western_Xia" title="Western Xia">Western Xia</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Spouse</th><td><div class="plainlist ">
