inger 1997, pg. 114</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Lane1-31" id="cite_note-Lane1-31"><a href="./Genghis_Khan#cite_ref-Lane1_31-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Lane1-31" class="mw-reference-text">Lane 2004, pg. xxvii</span></li><li about="#cite_note-32" id="cite_note-32"><a href="./Genghis_Khan#cite_ref-32" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-32" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt79" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"first":{"wt":"Jack"},"last":{"wt":"Weatherford"},"title":{"wt":"Genghis Khan and the Making of the Modern World"},"date":{"wt":"2005"},"publisher":{"wt":"Crown"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-307-23781-1"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBYk">Weatherford, Jack (2005). <i id="mwBYo">Genghis Khan and the Making of the Modern World</i>. Crown. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwBYs">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBYw"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-307-23781-1" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-307-23781-1" id="mwBY0">978-0-307-23781-1</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Genghis+Khan+and+the+Making+of+the+Modern+World&amp;rft.pub=Crown&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-307-23781-1&amp;rft.aulast=Weatherford&amp;rft.aufirst=Jack&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGenghis+Khan" class="Z3988" about="#mwt79" id="mwBY4"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt79" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBY8"/><!--|accessdate=January 28, 