<td colspan="3" style="border-top: 5px solid #FFD700; text-align:center;"><div>Genghis Khan </div><div><b><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Borjigin" title="Borjigin">House of Borjigin</a> (1206–1635)</b></div><span style="white-space:nowrap; font-size:90%; margin:2em"><b>Born:</b>  c. 1162</span><span style="white-space:nowrap; font-size:90%; margin:2em"><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><b>Died:</b>  1227</span><figure-inline typeof="mw:Image"><a href="./File:Borjigit_1.png"><img resource="./File:Borjigit_1.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bb/Borjigit_1.png/24px-Borjigit_1.png" data-file-width="59" data-file-height="108" data-file-type="bitmap" height="44" width="24" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bb/Borjigit_1.png/48px-Borjigit_1.png 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bb/Borjigit_1.png/36px-Borjigit_1.png 1.5x"/></a></figure-inline></td></tr>
