<td style="width: 40%; text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Khamag_Mongol" title="Khamag Mongol"><i>Khagan</i> of Khamag Mongol</a></b><br/>1189–1206</td>
