<div role="navigation" class="navbox" aria-labelledby="List_of_emperors_of_the_Yuan_dynasty" style="padding:3px" about="#mwt504" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Yuan Emperors","href":"./Template:Yuan_Emperors"},"params":{},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBwI"><table class="nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner" style="border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit"><tbody><tr><th scope="col" class="navbox-title" colspan="3"><div class="plainlinks hlist navbar mini"><ul><li class="nv-view"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template:Yuan_emperors" title="Template:Yuan emperors"><abbr title="View this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;">v</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-talk"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template_talk:Yuan_emperors" title="Template talk:Yuan emperors"><abbr title="Discuss this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;">t</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Yuan_emperors&amp;action=edit"><abbr title="Edit this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id="List_of_emperors_of_the_Yuan_dynasty" style="font-size:114%;margin:0 4em"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./List_of_emperors_of_the_Yuan_dynasty" title="List of emperors of the Yuan dynasty" class="mw-redirect">List of emperors</a> of the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Yuan_dynasty" title="Yuan dynasty">Yuan dynasty</a></div></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Yuan_dynasty" title="Yuan dynasty">Yuan</a></th><td class="navbox-list navbox-odd hlist" style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px"><div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><span style="font-size:85%;"><b>Early Mongol rulers posthumously promoted by </b><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Kublai_Khan" title="Kublai Khan">Kublai Khan</a><b> as Yuan emperors</b></span>
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Genghis_Khan" title="Genghis Khan">Taizu</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Tolui" title="Tolui">Ruizong</a> (regent)</li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ögedei_Khan" title="Ögedei Khan">Taizong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Güyük_Khan" title="Güyük Khan">Dingzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Möngke_Khan" title="Möngke Khan">Xianzong</a></li></ul>

<p><span style="font-size:85%;"><b>Enthronement of Kublai Khan in 1260 as <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Khagan" title="Khagan">Khagan</a>, officially assuming the role of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Emperor_of_China" title="Emperor of China">Emperor of China</a> as Yuan Shizu starting in 1271. Following <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Mongol_conquest_of_the_Song_dynasty" title="Mongol conquest of the Song dynasty">conquest</a> of Southern <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Song_dynasty" title="Song dynasty">Song dynasty</a> in 1279 ruled all of China</b></span></p>
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Kublai_Khan" title="Kublai Khan">Shizu</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Temür_Khan" title="Temür Khan">Chengzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Külüg_Khan" title="Külüg Khan">Wuzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ayurbarwada_Buyantu_Khan" title="Ayurbarwada Buyantu Khan">Renzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Gegeen_Khan" title="Gegeen Khan">Yingzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Yesün_Temür_(Yuan_dynasty)" title="Yesün Temür (Yuan dynasty)">Taiding Emperor</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ragibagh_Khan" title="Ragibagh Khan">Tianshun Emperor</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Jayaatu_Khan_Tugh_Temür" title="Jayaatu Khan Tugh Temür">Wenzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Khutughtu_Khan_Kusala" title="Khutughtu Khan Kusala">Mingzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Rinchinbal_Khan" title="Rinchinbal Khan">Ningzong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Toghon_Temür" title="Toghon Temür">Huizong (Emperor Shun)</a></li></ul></div></td><td class="navbox-image" rowspan="2" style="width:1px;padding:0px 0px 0px 2px"><div><span style="font-size:36px;">元</span></div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Northern_Yuan" title="Northern Yuan" class="mw-redirect">Northern Yuan</a></th><td class="navbox-list navbox-even hlist" style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px"><div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Toghon_Temür" title="Toghon Temür">Huizong (Emperor Shun)</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Biligtü_Khan_Ayushiridara" title="Biligtü Khan Ayushiridara">Zhaozong</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Uskhal_Khan_Tögüs_Temür" title="Uskhal Khan Tögüs Temür">Yizong (Emperor Mo)</a></li></ul>
