e:Yuan emperors">Yuan</a> → <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template:Ming_emperors" title="Template:Ming emperors">Ming</a> → <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template:Qing_emperors" title="Template:Qing emperors">Qing</a> → <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template:Presidents_of_the_Republic_of_China" title="Template:Presidents of the Republic of China">ROC</a> / <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template:Paramount_leaders_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China" title="Template:Paramount leaders of the People's Republic of China">PRC</a></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
